body.p:
For example, to change the label  and numbering for
      tables:.table--title-label{
  display:none;
}

*[class ~= "topic/table"] > caption:before{
  content: "Table " counter(tablecount) ". ";
}
      In a similar way, you can alter the labels for notes:

body.codeblock:
*[class ~= "topic/note"] > span.note__title {
  display:none;
}

*[class ~= "topic/note"]:before {
  content:" Note: ";
}
*[class ~= "topic/note"][type="caution"]:before {
  content: "Caution: ";
}
*[class ~= "topic/note"][type="important"]:before {
  content: "Important: ";
}
...
